# Hermes Core

```bash
hermes-core schema -o schema.json --config test/yaml/basic_config.hermes
```

```bash
hermes-core run test/yaml/basic_config.hermes
```


# push to pypi (poetry)
```bash
poetry build
poetry publish
```

pipy auth
```bash
c <token>
```

